{"word":"ἀσθένεια","slug":"ἀσθένεια","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀσθένεια</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀσθενής'><el>ἀσθενής</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>want of strength, weakness, feebleness, sickliness</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἀσθένεια βίου</el> poverty, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>sickness, a disease</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}